  <brief_title>Nicorandil Study to Reduce Cardiac Death After Percutaneous Coronary Intervention (PCI) in Hemodialysis Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Oral Nicorandil to Reduce Cardiac Death After Coronary Revascularization in Hemodialysis Patients: A Randomized Trial</official_title>
  <sponsors>
